Summary: Large bright green oval shaped object, shooting across the sky, no tail.
divs: Sighting DetailsOn the way to work one morning in Nov, traveling along hwy 121 between napa and sonoma i saw something strange....I've seen lots of shooting stars before, this was no shooting star. Bright green, not decending to the ground, but across the horizon. The speed was not that of a shooting star either, slower...then gone...only posting this because someone else reported seeing something like this......
